ps://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fecc9931a-44b0-4f67-b23c-d9c28a4f52e7_798x581.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：国际货币基金组织</figcaption></figure></div><p>这里的数字以百万美元为单位。</p><p>这里的基本故事是，无论有没有印度加入，新同盟国的国内生产总值都比新轴心国高得多。当我们使用 PPP 时，差异略有缩小，比率为 1.7，而不是 2.3（不包括印度）。从这个比较中我们看到的另一件事是，从经济和人口角度来看，新轴心主要是中国。</p><p>当然，我们可以预期这些数字会因战争、制裁、供应链中断、金融市场变化、战争生产和其他各种因素而发生变化。因此，这只是我们立场的指示性衡量标准。</p><p>但无论如何，为你的军队付费是一回事，但如果你的联盟实际上无法制造打仗所需的东西，那么拥有一堆美元就没那么有用了。现代战争需要制造很多东西——导弹、无人机、舰船、坦克、卡车、弹药等等。因此，制造业产出可能比简单的 GDP 更重要。当战争爆发时，来自旅游业或销售优质葡萄酒的美元将不如工厂产出的美元有用。无论如何，这是比较，同样以百万美元为单位： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ef93386-7f80-42f5-aea0-d2070d869efb_797x574.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ef93386-7f80-42f5-aea0-d2070d869efb_797x574.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ef93386-7f80-42f5-aea0-d2070d869efb_797x574.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ef93386-7f80-42f5-aea0-d2070d869efb_797x574.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ef93386-7f80-42f5-aea0-d2070d869efb_797x574.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ef93386-7f80-42f5-aea0-d2070d869efb_797x574.png" width="797" height="574" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://bucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/8ef93386-7f80-42f5-aea0-d2070d869efb_797x574.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:574,&quot;width&quot;:797,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:16214,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ef93386-7f80-42f5-aea0-d2070d869efb_797x574.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ef93386-7f80-42f5-aea0-d2070d869efb_797x574.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ef93386-7f80-42f5-aea0-d2070d869efb_797x574.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ef93386-7f80-42f5-aea0-d2070d869efb_797x574.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：世界银行</figcaption></figure></div><p>在这里我们看到这是一个更接近的事情。印度的制造量并不大，因此无论有没有印度，新同盟国的制造量都勉强超过了新轴心国。</p><p>原因和以前一样，是中国。正如马达明所说，中国已经成为“<a href="https://twitter.com/damienics/status/1278114690871300101">万物皆可制造的国家</a>”。在世纪之交之前，就价值而言，世界上很大一部分制造业是在美国、欧洲和日本等老工业化经济体中完成的。但在过去20年里，中国已成为第二个制造业中心，可与所有老牌工业化国家的<em>总和</em>相媲美。在某种程度上，我怀疑这种转变是我们看到大国冲突死灰复燃的原因。</p><p>这意味着，虽然俄罗斯本身无法生产用于与欧洲发生旷日持久的局部冲突的物资，但中国可以制造足够的物资来维持自己<em>和</em>俄罗斯在我在这里设想的两个集团之间的冲突。</p><h4>具体经济能力</h4><p><em>“北方可以制造蒸汽机、机车或火车车厢；你几乎无法制作一码布或一双鞋。” ——威廉·T·谢尔曼</em></p><p>上一节中的制造比较非常广泛；总增加值数字遗漏了很多重要的东西。它没有告诉我们一个国家的武器系统技术有多先进。它没有告诉我们百分之多少的制造能力可以重新用于军事用途。</p><p>最重要的是，它并不能显示一个国家的供应链有多完整。如果你与依赖敌国提供关键零部件的制造公司发生战争，那么无论你在和平时期生产多少附加值，你的工厂都会陷入停顿。和平时期的附加值是按边际计算的，而战时的制造能力是<em>超边际的</em>——这是在发生痛苦的变化使你与和平时期的供应链隔绝后你能赚到的金额。在新冠大流行初期，当美国发现自己无法生产足够的口罩、新冠检测试剂或呼吸机时<a href="https://www.fda.gov/medical-devices/coronavirus-covid-19-and-medical-devices/medical-device-shortages-during-covid-19-public-health-emergency">，痛苦地重新发现了这一原则</a>。但在疫情后期，美国拥有先进的生物技术供应链，可以生产大量 mRNA 疫苗，而<a href="https://www.modernhealthcare.com/supply-chain/chinas-bet-homegrown-mrna-vaccines-holds-back-nation">中国则陷入困境</a>。</p><p>因此，很难判断哪些供应链部分最终将成为冲突的瓶颈。这就是为什么拜登政府正在<a href="https://www.pwc.com/us/en/services/consulting/cybersecurity-risk-regulatory/library/biden-executive-order-supply-chain.html">积极</a>解决这个问题，我相信中国当局也在做同样的事情。但我们可以预测有一些事情会很重要。</p><p>首先，燃料。 （此时，我将停止制作堆积条形图，只显示地图。）我们可以看到，两个假定的集团都拥有充足的石油资源： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F46b0bc4e-cfab-40be-9fc5-2027b1432a43_6460x3480.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F46b0bc4e-cfab-40be-9fc5-2027b1432a43_6460x3480.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F46b0bc4e-cfab-40be-9fc5-2027b1432a43_6460x3480.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F46b0bc4e-cfab-40be-9fc5-2027b1432a43_6460x3480.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F46b0bc4e-cfab-40be-9fc5-2027b1432a43_6460x3480.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F46b0bc4e-cfab-40be-9fc5-2027b1432a43_6460x3480.jpeg" width="1456" height="784" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://bucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/46b0bc4e-cfab-40be-9fc5-2027b1432a43_6460x3480.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:784,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:2566945,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;By Jo Di Graphics - Own work, CC BY-SA 4.0, https://commons.wikimedia.org/w/index.php?curid=68942982&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;By Jo Di Graphics - Own work, CC BY-SA 4.0, https://commons.wikimedia.org/w/index.php?curid=68942982&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="By Jo Di Graphics - Own work, CC BY-SA 4.0, https://commons.wikimedia.org/w/index.php?curid=68942982" title="作者：Jo Di Graphics - 自己的作品，CC BY-SA 4.0，https://commons.wikimedia.org/w/index.php?curid=68942982" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F46b0bc4e-cfab-40be-9fc5-2027b1432a43_6460x3480.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F46b0bc4e-cfab-40be-9fc5-2027b1432a43_6460x3480.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F46b0bc4e-cfab-40be-9fc5-2027b1432a43_6460x3480.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F46b0bc4e-cfab-40be-9fc5-2027b1432a43_6460x3480.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_countries_by_coal_reserves">煤炭的情况也类似</a>——中国和俄罗斯的煤炭储量充足，美国和澳大利亚的煤炭储量也充足。气也<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_countries_by_natural_gas_proven_reserves">大致相似</a>。</p><p>因此，从表面上看，两个集团都拥有足够的化石燃料。对于新轴心来说，问题主要是俄罗斯能否向中国提供足够的石油和天然气——这将涉及要么将大量油轮运送到可能有争议的水域，要么在广阔的欧亚大陆上建造大量非常昂贵、困难的管道。当然，美国在向其欧洲和亚洲盟友提供石油、煤炭和天然气方面也将面临类似的问题。</p><p>当然，化石燃料并不是唯一的能源类型。还有可再生能源。运输可再生能源需要大量电池（可能还需要一些电解槽），而这又需要大量矿物质。大卫·罗伯茨（David Roberts）对替代能源的<a href="https://www.volts.wtf/p/minerals-and-the-clean-energy-transition#details">矿物需求进行了详细分析</a>，并用一些很好的图表显示了矿物的位置。石墨和稀土集中在中国，而钴和铂集中在非洲： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5cddcb5f-c7d6-4229-a5c1-e47c908b3a1a_1456x666.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5cddcb5f-c7d6-4229-a5c1-e47c908b3a1a_1456x666.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5cddcb5f-c7d6-4229-a5c1-e47c908b3a1a_1456x666.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5cddcb5f-c7d6-4229-a5c1-e47c908b3a1a_1456x666.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5cddcb5f-c7d6-4229-a5c1-e47c908b3a1a_1456x666.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5cddcb5f-c7d6-4229-a5c1-e47c908b3a1a_1456x666.png" width="1456" height="666" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://bucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/5cddcb5f-c7d6-4229-a5c1-e47c908b3a1a_1456x666.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:666,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:354059,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5cddcb5f-c7d6-4229-a5c1-e47c908b3a1a_1456x666.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5cddcb5f-c7d6-4229-a5c1-e47c908b3a1a_1456x666.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5cddcb5f-c7d6-4229-a5c1-e47c908b3a1a_1456x666.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5cddcb5f-c7d6-4229-a5c1-e47c908b3a1a_1456x666.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://www.volts.wtf/p/minerals-and-the-clean-energy-transition#details">Volts</a> 、IEA</figcaption></figure></div><p>当然，这只是目前的产量。如果有必要的话，美国及其盟国可能会开发国内稀土和石墨供应，就像日本在中国切断<a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2021-02-22/china-weaponizing-rare-earths-technology-will-probably-backfire">稀土供应后开始开采稀土</a>一样。但寻找和利用这些资源需要时间，因此新盟友现在可能应该考虑这一点。</p><p>然后是矿物在哪里加工的问题。在这里我们看到答案大多是“中国”： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8310900a-6f15-4bb7-82f4-91bc5c6c1883_2134x968.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8310900a-6f15-4bb7-82f4-91bc5c6c1883_2134x968.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8310900a-6f15-4bb7-82f4-91bc5c6c1883_2134x968.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8310900a-6f15-4bb7-82f4-91bc5c6c1883_2134x968.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8310900a-6f15-4bb7-82f4-91bc5c6c1883_2134x968.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8310900a-6f15-4bb7-82f4-91bc5c6c1883_2134x968.png" width="1456" height="660" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://bucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/8310900a-6f15-4bb7-82f4-91bc5c6c1883_2134x968.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:660,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:95753,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8310900a-6f15-4bb7-82f4-91bc5c6c1883_2134x968.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8310900a-6f15-4bb7-82f4-91bc5c6c1883_2134x968.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8310900a-6f15-4bb7-82f4-91bc5c6c1883_2134x968.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8310900a-6f15-4bb7-82f4-91bc5c6c1883_2134x968.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://www.volts.wtf/p/minerals-and-the-clean-energy-transition#details">Volts</a> 、IEA</figcaption></figure></div><p>对于新盟友来说，这似乎是一个真正的弱点。我的怀疑是，发达国家懒惰地让许多其他基本的“第一产业”类型的任务集体迁移到中国，因为它们在价值链上不是很高。但在发生冲突的情况下，“价值链上游”的意义突然就小了很多。</p><p>半导体（即计算机芯片）是另一个考虑因素。正如他们所说，“芯片是新石油”，这意味着几乎所有机械都使用半导体。这包括所有战争机器和战争生产。目前，新盟友生产了世界上大部分的半导体，尽管中国正在奋起直追： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4f422191-4271-4f59-a3b4-bd9eb2940684_1200x1200.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4f422191-4271-4f59-a3b4-bd9eb2940684_1200x1200.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4f422191-4271-4f59-a3b4-bd9eb2940684_1200x1200.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4f422191-4271-4f59-a3b4-bd9eb2940684_1200x1200.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4f422191-4271-4f59-a3b4-bd9eb2940684_1200x1200.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4f422191-4271-4f59-a3b4-bd9eb2940684_1200x1200.jpeg" width="1200" height="1200" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://bucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/4f422191-4271-4f59-a3b4-bd9eb2940684_1200x1200.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1200,&quot;width&quot;:1200,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:403871,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4f422191-4271-4f59-a3b4-bd9eb2940684_1200x1200.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4f422191-4271-4f59-a3b4-bd9eb2940684_1200x1200.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4f422191-4271-4f59-a3b4-bd9eb2940684_1200x1200.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4f422191-4271-4f59-a3b4-bd9eb2940684_1200x1200.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>但尽管中国付出了最大的努力，新盟友在未来十年仍将在这一领域保持决定性优势。</p><p>总的来说，审视供应链的瓶颈向我们表明，新轴心国和新同盟国都不是一个完全独立、一体化的经济机器，无法制造重大冲突所需的一切。过去20年，中国与老牌工业化国家发展了共生关系，紧密相连。 （人们希望这足以防止冲突，但鉴于过去的经验，这几乎肯定是一厢情愿的想法。）</p><p>这意味着，一旦发生冲突，每个集团都将争先恐后地弥补自己的弱点——中国争先恐后地建造更多芯片工厂，并从俄罗斯、美国和欧洲获得更多石油，而日本则争先恐后地重建低水平国家。重视他们外包给中国的第一产业。</p><h4>有史以来最激烈的经济竞争</h4><p>我不能说新轴心国是否是美国及其盟友所面临的最强大的军事竞争对手。最初的轴心国无疑是可怕的，苏联拥有<a href="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bb/US_and_USSR_nuclear_stockpiles.svg/2560px-US_and_USSR_nuclear_stockpiles.svg.png">数以万计</a>的核武器，只需按一下按钮即可烘烤世界。但我认为，上述比较表明，新轴心无疑代表了美国及其盟友从未遇到过的<em>经济</em>竞争对手。原因很简单，就是中国。俄罗斯主要是一个拥有核武器的加油站。但中国有以下三点优势：</p><ol><li><p>中国的工人比原来的轴心国或苏联集团多得多。</p></li><li><p>中国拥有先进的制造技术，相对而言可能可以与原来的轴心国相媲美，并且远远超过苏联集团。</p></li><li><p>中国拥有世界上最大的制造业集群，使其成为“制造一切的国家”，这是轴心国和苏联都未能做到的。</p></li></ol><p>这简直是​​近代史上绝无仅有的情况。工业革命始于欧洲，并蔓延到美国和东亚边缘地区。二战结束后，中欧和东亚边缘地区并入了以美国为首的联盟，该联盟以共产主义列强永远无法威胁的方式主导了全球制造业。现在，随着中国的崛起，世界制造业大致一分为二。</p><p>因此，美国（及其盟国）的战时经济大部分将是为了重新发现他们在中国迅速崛起期间忽视的制造能力。 </p><div><hr></div><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?"><span>现在订阅</span></a></p><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/sizing-up-the-new-axis?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"> <a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/sizing-up-the-new-axis?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share"><span>分享</span></a></p><p></p>;
